data.description: This wonderful property is located behind the gates at the Eagles Landing Country Club, overlooking the 5th fairway and green. This is a remarkable opportunity to live within the country club community and to live on the golf course! The back patio is a perfect place to relax and listen to the sound of the water in the koi pond and watch the golfers navigate the 5th hole or to watch wildlife take over the course in the evening. This home has the owner's suite on the main level and the second floor has two bedrooms, a Jack and Jill bath, and a large loft area that can be used for multiple purposes. The spacious kitchen has an island and lots of counter and cupboard space. Check out the pictures and virtual tour!
